<item>
            <title>[LU-11162] run_lfsck() is not functional on suites where check_and_setup_lustre() is not called</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11162</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;

run_lfsck () {

...

&#160;&#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; wait_update_facet --verbose mds${k} &quot;$LCTL get_param -n \

&#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; mdd.$(facet_svc mds${k}).lfsck_layout |

...

&#160;&#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; wait_update_facet --verbose mds${k} &quot;$LCTL get_param -n \

&#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; mdd.$(facet_svc mds${k}).lfsck_namespace |

}

facet_svc() {

&#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; local facet=$1

&#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; local &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;var&lt;/span&gt;=${facet}_svc&#160;

&#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; echo -n ${!&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;var&lt;/span&gt;}

}

&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;${facet}_svc is initialized here :&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;

check_and_setup_lustre() -&amp;gt;&#160;init_facets_vars() -&amp;gt; init_facet_vars()

&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;performance-sanity does not call&#160;check_and_setup_lustre(), all performance-sanity tests run with LFSCK_ALWAYS=yes fail as&#160;:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;

== performance-sanity test complete, duration 169 sec ================================================ 09:24:18 (1531905858)

fre1233: error: get_param: param_path &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;mdd&lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;//lfsck_layout&apos;&lt;/span&gt;: No such file or directory
&lt;/span&gt;
fre1233: error: get_param: param_path &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;mdd&lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;//lfsck_layout&apos;&lt;/span&gt;: No such file or directory
&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
